						<div class="postbody">My thoughts.<br /><br />-256 color choices (vs current 50ish), 8 or 16 per palette<br />-per tile palette selection, and BG tile flipping<br /><br />Larger sprites (16x16) and more per line<br /><br />More RAM...32k<br /><br />Music, 8 pulse channels, finer volume control<br />-1 full PCM audio channel<br /><br />Faster processor. 65c02. They make 14 Mhz today, that's<br />8x faster than NES.</div>

					
